# ** What is the motivation for the change?
# ** How does it address the problem?
# ** Are there any side effects?

# Closes #123, #245...

# *** Types reminder ***
# feat (new feature for the user, not a new feature for build script)
# fix (bug fix for the user, *not a fix to a build script*)
# docs (changes to the documentation)
# style (formatting, missing semi colons, lint...)
# refactor (a code that neither fix bug or adds a feature, eg. moving functions)
# test (new tests, refactoring tests; no production code change)
# chore (change not visible by the users (e.g. CI, gitignore...)
